title: This guy's live Daft Punk 'Harder Better Faster Stronger' cover is incredible
text:
We used to think that all that vocal jumping was all fancy post-production from the French duo but turns out we were wrong.
Lorenz Rhode and his talkbox-synthesizer combo proves not only is it possibly to cover the Daft Punk hit live, it's also hella cool to watch and hear. Still such a tune.
Via YouTube
